<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png"
    href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Aceship/Arknight-Images/main/avatars/char_150_snakek.png">

<head>
    <title>ArkPRTS</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="description" content="View in-game arknights information updated real-time.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="arknights search real-time">
</head>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="static/style.css">


<body>
    <br>
    <div class="simple-border">
        Enter your Yostar email to login and click "Send code".
        You will receive a code in your email.
        Enter the code in the box below and click "Login".
        <br>
        The server will only send the browser a cookie with your token.
        Nothing is stored.
        <br>
        WARNING: Viewing your user data will kick you out of arknights!
        Arknights does not allow multiple connections to the same account.
        <br>
        <form action="/login" method="GET">
            <label for="server">Server:</label>
            <select name="server">
                <option value="en">EN</option>
                <option value="jp">JP</option>
                <option value="kr">KR</option>
            </select>
            <br>
            <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="Yostar email" required
                value="{{ request.query.get('email', '') }}">
            <br>
            <input type="code" name="code" placeholder="email code">
            <input type="submit" value="Send code">
            <br>
            <input type="submit" value="Login">
        </form>
        <br>
        {% if error %}
        <b>ERROR:</b> {{ error }}
        <p>Please ensure you aren't using the wrong email address, an old code, or that arknights isn't currently undergoing maintenance</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    <br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>
    <footer>
    If you happen to keep getting logged out it's possible that the server is out-of-date.<br>
    If search is broken, then login is definitely broken too.
    </footer>
</body>

</html>